  <div class="row" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
    <div class="col-md-4" style="flex: 0 0 30%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <div class="card" style="width: 100%;">
        <img src="/img/project2.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Project 1" style="width: 420px; height: 195px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">I participated in a group project that applied Agile methodologies for project management. Our goal was to plan and conceptualize a travel assistant app collaboratively. We adopted Agile principles to improve teamwork, prioritize features, and iterate efficiently, resulting in a well-structured project plan aligned with user needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4" style="flex: 0 0 30%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
