        <img src="/img/webdesign.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Project 2" style="width: 420px; height: 195px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Conceptualized, designed, and developed a visually appealing and user-friendly marketing website. 
            Utilized HTML and CSS to create an interactive and responsive site.
            Incorporated property listings, high-quality images, and relevant information to showcase the real estate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4" style="flex: 0 0 30%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <div class="card" style="width: 100%;">
        <img src="/img/project3.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Project 3" style="width: 420px; height: 195px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">I collaborated on a MySQL database project for a clothing store. Our team designed and built a database to manage inventory, customer data, and orders. We focused on data integrity and efficiency, creating a valuable asset for the store's operations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
